# correlation of response to alpha-amanitin and new mRNA production (Fig. 2E and S2C)

# Changes in alpha-amanitin-treated samples are checked for total mRNA levels. Usually, there is a delay between the start of new mRNA production and changes in total mRNA levels.
# Therefore, rather than comparing the same time points of two experiments, we analyse subsequent time points.

# plot for 6h alpha-amanitin treatment and 3h labelling (Fig. S2C)
